
This is the python file which will run on RPi and will act as a server. RPi will fetch the user name and the login id of registered user, from 
the data base. whenever user will enter the login id as a password in mobile app then that will go to RPi and that password will be check, whether 
the user password is correct or not. if password will be correct then scan opention will pop up and then user will scan to open or close the door. When 
user will scan then that scanned information and login password will send to RPi and it will check that persion is accessing the alloted 
room or not.
